{"tid":957040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人想貪埋日本個醫療保險","createTime":"2018-12-26T17:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T11:40:10.000Z","uid":5818,"like":275,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"bce782733aed4c183714ca372f7c3c0740b1f927","tid":957040,"uid":5818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T17:34:47.000Z","msg":"話說喺twitter 見到有人post 咗段抖陰片，大概係話日本有國民健康保險，有嗰張保險卡就可以以3折睇醫生，長期病嘅治療只需要一個月幾百蚊人民幣左右。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0GCnfAn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0GCnfAn.png&h=d6256645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPost嗰位網民就話好多人移民過日本就係為咗享受依種福利，結果引起日本網民嘅不滿，叫班支那人咪撚移民過嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用我啲垃圾日本翻譯下<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oRSuE21.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoRSuE21.png&h=6e1f043d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依種制度係日本人努力工作嘅成果嚟<br />\n如果要益埋你哋嘅話，你哋就要設立反相同嘅制度。如果支那無幫助日本人嘅制度嘅話，咁我哋都唔會益支那人<br />\n<br />\n根本唔應該用我哋日本人納嘅稅去幫外國人<br />\n國家唔應該袖手旁觀，希望國家諗下對策<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q572Z22.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ572Z22.png&h=f1df4f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係唔敢相信你哋會移民到其他國家！你哋唔係有從祖先傳落嚟嘅土地咩？你哋唔通唔會為咗自己國家仆心仆命咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你班支那人口中嗰套愛國愛黨去撚咗邊到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n移民去小日本叫愛國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3cb59678cdac0cb5908578a2f346790d8daa4f1","tid":957040,"uid":5818,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T17:35:34.000Z","msg":"補返條link先<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/eggtokyo/status/1077089099708719104\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Feggtokyo%2Fstatus%2F1077089099708719104&d=2CaonD1R7l1%2BjX2bZM9IycVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=aa2f5507\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Feggtokyo%2Fstatus%2F1077089099708719104&h=7d909858\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/eggtokyo/status/1077089099708719104</a>"},{"pid":"1c657578f072ccd413c0b3986962bb2945d6da26","tid":957040,"uid":3646,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T20:29:47.000Z","msg":"知又點<br />\n政府會做野咩？"},{"pid":"20fb36f7892608d4b105a0af588bf0e61b448691","tid":957040,"uid":11598,"like":111,"dislike":1,"score":110,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T20:39:05.000Z","msg":"香港咪一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本支那人係要管 管唔到 咪周圍搞屎棍"},{"pid":"c77f2e0e93f058ab7604ea39ee557b36701eab3b","tid":957040,"uid":79410,"like":130,"dislike":1,"score":129,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T20:42:01.000Z","msg":"日本藉咁難入. 冇日日150隻木馬入侵<br />\n要收支那皮基本上好易."},{"pid":"f6e93e14f37b034a4d1e16c9a58fc6b4c38baa21","tid":957040,"uid":189160,"like":4,"dislike":21,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T21:01:43.000Z","msg":"連登仔咪一撚樣日日發夢做美國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一撚樣姐"},{"pid":"3912d3b2780348424c4ab0e8e07f98957a6e05b0","tid":957040,"uid":42283,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"quote":{"pid":"1c657578f072ccd413c0b3986962bb2945d6da26","tid":957040,"uid":3646,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T20:29:47.000Z","msg":"知又點<br />\n政府會做野咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T21:04:34.000Z","msg":"日本既話，會"},{"pid":"55bd498a55201b5643429751421d0070774c5239","tid":957040,"uid":42283,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"quote":{"pid":"f6e93e14f37b034a4d1e16c9a58fc6b4c38baa21","tid":957040,"uid":18